# Instructions to run the game

Open your terminal and navigate to the `SourceFiles` directory:
`cd SourceFiles`

## If you have make installed
-> Run the following command to compile and execute the project:
`make run`

## If you don't have make installed
-> Compile the source files individually: 
`g++ -c main.cpp "CppFiles/*.cpp" -I "../SFML/include" `

-> Link the object files to create the executable: 
`g++ main.o Game.o MainMenu.o Player.o Chest.o EasyChest.o MediumChest.o HardChest.o Paper.o -o main -L "../SFML/lib" -lsfml-graphics -lsfml-window -lsfml-system`

-> Run the application:
`./main`
